{"tid":1703230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反抗 唔好得個講","createTime":"2019-11-10T07:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T09:56:33.000Z","uid":214810,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1555eb1b9f9a0b50856a9b55650bbe5a24ddd28a","tid":1703230,"uid":214810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"琴/尋日見隔離有個Po話戴口罩會比藍絲撩<br />\n<br />\n小弟今日做左個實測<br />\n路過地鐵站附近有中年男人刻意撞<br />\n吊你個肺我吸收隔離樓主經驗緊係唔撚忍<br />\n追番上去撞到佢電話都跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話一段 想講嘅係 <br />\n香港人反抗 報仇 唔係只係口號<br />\n遇到不滿不公要反抗係運動嘅本議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期一 三罷</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbEiOMu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcbEiOMu.jpg&h=ec283eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vghjS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vghjS9.jpg&h=bdfe4b25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzFuaZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzFuaZQ.jpg&h=f833c70f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFMdCER.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFMdCER.jpg&h=b7da7df3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EcE6XET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEcE6XET.jpg&h=a428a7a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 報仇</span>"},{"pid":"8180738c50c00293c7976473ef45ff1de7565fc0","tid":1703230,"uid":214810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:33:21.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"bbd95e3898a03fe4ae21beffcd105108c612f32b","tid":1703230,"uid":214810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"9ee2ca2ba86f3637505166cdd5a07e30e34551e0","tid":1703230,"uid":214810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor